e color in future rounds. Actions allow players to gain wealth, which can be traded for influence in the city. Performing various actions also earns bonuses and enhances actions even more as the game proceeds. The player who scores the most points by the end of the game wins.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><img src=\"https://cf.geekdo-images.com/zSMdU8DMBBvW2LIOjVCM7A__itemrep/img/-RnOaoGEX9YStxHqYm3x4Vvk8Nc=/fit-in/246x300/filters:strip_icc()/pic6289695.jpg\" alt=\"Marrakesh image\"></p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th align=\"right\">Players</th>\n<th align=\"right\">Min. Age</th>\n<th align=\"right\">Time</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"right\">2 - 4</td>\n<td align=\"right\">14+</td>\n<td align=\"right\">120m</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>","updatedAt":"2021-10-01T01:57:16.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"ellisonleao/magictools","categoryHTML":"<h2>Code</h2><h3>Engines and Frameworks</h3>","itemHTML":"<li>🎉 <a href=\"https://stride3d.net/\">Stride</a> - Open Source C# Game Engine.</li>","updatedAt":"2021-10-01T01:55:11.000Z"}]}},"pageContext":{"type":"day","from":1633046400000,"to":1633132799999,"previousId":"2021-10-02","nextId":"2021-09-30","nextName":"Sep 30th, 2021","previousName":"Oct 2nd, 2021"}},"staticQueryHashes":["228695001","2744905544","2828988102"]}